text: The Margherita Pizza was absolutely delicious! The crust was crispy and the sauce perfect.
Caesar Salad was fresh and tasty. Great portion size.
Pad Thai was excellent - authentic flavors and perfect spice level.
Pasta Alfredo tasted great but the portion could be larger.
Veg Biryani was absolutely outstanding! Will definitely order again.
Chicken Wings were crispy and flavorful. Highly recommend!
The burger was mediocre - patty was dry and cold.
Sushi Rolls were fresh and beautifully presented. Loved it!
Fries were tasty but a bit too salty for my liking.
Margherita Pizza again - consistent quality every time!
Caesar Salad was okay but could use more dressing.
Pad Thai was good but the noodles were slightly overcooked.
Pasta Alfredo - creamy and delicious. My favorite!
Veg Biryani disappointed me this time. Not as good as before.
Chicken Wings - best wings in town! Always crispy and hot.
The burger had great flavor this time. Much better!
Sushi Rolls ordered again - never disappoints.
Fries were perfectly cooked and seasoned just right.
Margherita Pizza is my go-to order every time.
Caesar Salad - quick service and fresh ingredients.
Tandoori chicken was perfectly spiced.
